{"tid":445743,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"不要把「前衛」當成工藝未成熟的借口","createTime":"2017-10-23T15:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T15:48:08.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf94e8dc313907beb6275e7e1e75f6a60919f463","tid":445743,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://mings.mpweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/2017-10-23_17-38-56.jpg.pagespeed.ce.k4nJ8tIe7l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmings.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F2017-10-23_17-38-56.jpg.pagespeed.ce.k4nJ8tIe7l.jpg&h=28f97c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周的Amazon Fashion Week Tokyo中，新晉設計師Thibaut其一作品牽起熱話。各大外國網媒以&quot;Torn Jean&quot;為文章角度，暗嘲其設計（左圖）爛得過火，背部的臀部位置更是叫模特兒「原形畢露」。隨一陣子的嘲笑過後，放下「被」先入為主的觀感，退一步看，該設計其實叫筆者想到2017秋冬的Maison Margiela。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2h1iT5a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2h1iT5a&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=086a7edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2h1iT5a</a>"}]}